attr.title: Hyper Overlap 2: Turbo Edition
attr.desc: In the future year of 199X, the world was finally united in 7 grand cartridges. But one day, the [Glitch Wizard] decided to take it one step further! Play every game at once (not in a good way!) as you fight against the glitches and corruption.
attr.inst: Download the game from Itch.io and extract all files into the assets folder.
attr.inst_md: Download the game from [Itch.io](https://yaru.itch.io/hyper-overlap-2-turbo-edition) and extract all files into the `assets` folder.
